headline.main: McIlroy Eyes Regaining Number One World Ranking
headline.print_headline: McIlroy Eyes Regaining Number One World Ranking

lead_paragraph: Patience will be a virtue for Rory McIlroy on Sunday as he seeks to win the WGC-Mexico Championship and possibly regain the world number one ranking.
